Class TestManager

java.lang.Object
TestManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
TestTrade, TestTradingInfo
public class TestManager
extends java.lang.Object
This is used to help make accessing and modifying the database files to be easier, while giving the generic EntryNotFoundException more meaning.

This contains general methods that is useful in all applications.
